## üé® Applying Principles Together

### Example: DaysSelector Component

**Principle 1 (Automation)**: Auto-selects 7 days as default  
**Principle 2 (Accessibility)**: Voice input, keyboard shortcuts, screen reader labels  
**Principle 3 (Single-Screen)**: Inline on main page, no modal  
**Principle 4 (Instant Value)**: Shows immediately, no loading  
**Principle 5 (Graceful Degradation)**: Works without voice, fallback to buttons

### Example: Grocery List Display

**Principle 1 (Automation)**: Auto-generated, no manual editing  
**Principle 2 (Accessibility)**: Print-optimized, high contrast, keyboard accessible  
**Principle 3 (Single-Screen)**: Same page, scroll to see  
**Principle 4 (Instant Value)**: Shown immediately after generation  
**Principle 5 (Graceful Degradation)**: Cached if API fails, shows last generated list

