## ü§î Decision Framework

When making any design or development decision, ask:

1. **Does this automate a decision?** (Principle 1)
2. **Is this accessible to all users?** (Principle 2)
3. **Does this keep everything on one screen?** (Principle 3)
4. **Does this provide value immediately?** (Principle 4)
5. **Does this work if something fails?** (Principle 5)

If the answer to all 5 is "yes" ‚Üí ‚úÖ Proceed  
If any answer is "no" ‚Üí ü§î Reconsider or justify exception

